  "text": "We start with an overview of D-Wave design features and introduce notation that will be used throughout. For details about underlying technologies see Bunyk et al. [CITATION_1] , Dickson et al. [CITATION_2] , Harris et al. [CITATION_3] , Johnson et al. [CITATION_4] or Lanting et al. [CITATION_5] .",
